Description: Emacs Lisp package manager backed by the Nix store
 Nelix is a package manager configured in Emacs Lisp and backed by the
 Nix store.  It can install Linux user-space tools from nixpkgs and
 Emacs Lisp packages described by Nelix package definitions.
 .
 This package installs the Emacs Lisp interface.  It keeps compatibility
 aliases for the previous anvil-pkg name while exposing the new Nelix
 entry points such as nelix-install, nelix-search, and nelix-doctor.
